  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2007980/extras/8a5882f84076209667f6bff2b8942e6d.avif?t=1772417137\" width=780 height=78 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A world called Fillwitz has finally ushered in an era of peace after the long war between mankind and the demon.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >But Misty, who lives in the underground city of Gondalva and runs a blacksmith shop, is distressed by the sharp reduction in work caused by the peace.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >But before long, the opportunity comes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A huge underground city [Gehenna Cavity] was found near the town.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Attracted by the new resources and the legendary [Great Power], humans and Demons gathered here from all over the world.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Misty decided to seize this valuable business opportunity to revitalize the blacksmith shop, but she didn't expect a turning point in her fate!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2007980/extras/4d0004a7948f672ee1a39d007573a518.avif?t=1772417137\" width=780 height=78 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >JRPG</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Blacksmith system</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Skill tree </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Cooking</p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2007980/extras/8a5882f84076209667f6bff2b8942e6d.avif?t=1772417137\" width=780 height=78 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A world called Fillwitz has finally ushered in an era of peace after the long war between mankind and the demon.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >But Misty, who lives in the underground city of Gondalva and runs a blacksmith shop, is distressed by the sharp reduction in work caused by the peace.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >But before long, the opportunity comes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A huge underground city [Gehenna Cavity] was found near the town.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Attracted by the new resources and the legendary [Great Power], humans and Demons gathered here from all over the world.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Misty decided to seize this valuable business opportunity to revitalize the blacksmith shop, but she didn't expect a turning point in her fate!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2007980/extras/4d0004a7948f672ee1a39d007573a518.avif?t=1772417137\" width=780 height=78 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >JRPG</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Blacksmith system</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Skill tree </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Cooking</p></li></ul>",
